### sp_sc_cvar_escape

sp_sc_cvar_escape

Escape text

Character codes are replaced by %hh, where hh is the hexadecimal value of the character

Synopsis:

```txt
sp_sc_cvar_escape
DST CVAR

SRC CVAR

CHAR CODE...
```
Parameters:

- DST CVAR:
- SRC CVAR:
- CHAR CODE:
